PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of John Ronald Longstaffe, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending December 28, 1996, in the place of W.A.
